Package: rsmartcn
Type: Package
Title: R interface to the Java Chinese word segmentation system of smartcn
Version: 0.1-0
Date: 2012-06-12
Author: Ronggui HUANG
Maintainer: Ronggui HUANG<ronggui.huang@gmail.com>
Depends: rJava
Description: This package provides a function to segment a Chinese sentence into words which are seperated by space.It is mainly an interface to smartcn.
